Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:10.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:37.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on! Are you \Nfinished already, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:12.76,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.37,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:21.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm someone who was born without any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:25.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I'm going to \Nbecome the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:28.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:31.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to prove that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.24,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.05,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.37,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.75,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King protects everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:56.01,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,We were born to protect \Neveryone in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:01.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm going to lose \Nto someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:04.77,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.81,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, pebble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I may be just a pebble,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:16.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,a pebble that shatters diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:01.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:06.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:10.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:15.17,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:29.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:33.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:42.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:48.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.46,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.56,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of You
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this actually going \Nto keep him restrained?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is not so weak that it'd \Nbe broken by someone who's injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We've taken his grimoire, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so pissy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Want some medicinal herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.35,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.84,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be moving around now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.30,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.88,Default,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you protected me, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.44,Default,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.37,Default,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so helpless that \NI couldn't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.99,Default,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:16.33,Default,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,M-More importantly, Asta, \Ndo something about your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.84,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.28,Default,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.66,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you the one turning red?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.11,Default,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.84,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:33.64,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My robe's ripped to shreds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.34,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna's gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.85,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa will fix it for you when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.84,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's good, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:48.81,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,To think that we'd be saved \Nby the Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:56.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We were the first ones to arrive, \Ntherefore we win this competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:06:00.71,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but I will allow you three to enter \Nthe treasure chamber, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always sound \Nso arrogant, four-eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you very much, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're very welcome!\N Watch how you speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me, Lord Four-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "Lord Four-Eyes"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:19.21,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I don't have time to argue with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me, Lord Four-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.52,top,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.65,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They sure like wasting each other's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.18,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up and I'll break \Nthose glasses of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.84,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's just cruelty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that, Lord Four-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.66,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.49,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us head to the treasure chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:38.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the Clover Kingdom's Magic Knights\Nwho get to the treasure chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:39.83,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.18,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,How do you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some code to \Nopen this door somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! Think harder, four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.93,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.04,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It appears this door is made with magic,\Nso just cut through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.12,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Like, swoosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:15.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:19.72,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mountain of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Luck popped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.27,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:28.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you use this for.\NI haven't the slightest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.44,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,All of you! Stop touching \Nthings without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:37.28,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They might be magical items \Nworthy of being national treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit won't hurt, crabbypants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.04,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "crabbypants"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll just go back to "four-eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.89,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then "glasses man."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.29,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See? You {\i1}are{\i0} a crabbypants!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that makes you clever or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:13.82,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are these symbols?\NI've never seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The symbols...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.74,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go around touching things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:59.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow! Stop! \NYou're gonna tear it out, Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:09:59.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.64,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a rather rare, \Nstrange grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though it's stitched together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.72,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.48,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We have a four-leaf clover,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:27.74,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,and a grimoire so filthy\Nyou can't even read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.31,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I have three oddities on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.82,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything interesting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.24,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This power...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.50,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.73,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.91,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,My restraining magic... \NAnd in so little time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.49,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How could he have revived?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.49,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.24,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Flame recovery magic? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:31.25,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone should have only \None magical attribute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:39.03,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mages have mana from the four classical \Nelements: fire, wind, water, and earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:52.06,sign_16632_146_Fire,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,516)}Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:52.06,sign_16650_147_Wind,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,516)}Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:52.06,sign_16671_148_Water,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,516)}Water
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:52.06,sign_16689_149_Earth,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,516)}Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.32,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Fire is strong against wind, \Nand weak against water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.68,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There are compatibilities \Nbetween each element.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:49.14,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mages can only use magic \Nfrom their own mana or
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.93,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,from a single attribute derived from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:58.11,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's breaking all of those laws to have \Ntwo different kinds of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.64,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, he was clearly \Na user of offensive magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.48,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but now he's using recovery magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.79,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's inconceivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:09.88,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the results of the \NDiamond Kingdom's experiments?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.62,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll become a great warrior, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.46,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.31,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.39,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put that fire out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.23,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to my friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.07,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I know your abilities now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.21,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,If that blade is able to cut \Nthrough various magics,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.63,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,then what about magic that's \Nfaster than your blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.57,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.53,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to my friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.14,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:03.11,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive, \Nand the weak will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:04.84,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.36,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.25,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.38,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you idiot! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The Dream-Healing Flower \NCradle won't be fast enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.77,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Recovery Magic: \NPrincess-Healing Flower Robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.61,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the strongest \Nspell I can use right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.87,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.29,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.42,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.17,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Mimosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.58,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.93,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.43,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.94,flashback,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:31.00,flashback,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you'd be able to use \Nrecovery magic that's this powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:36.54,flashback,other,0000,0000,0000,,With your royal magic, you may become \Na healer who can heal any injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.76,flashback,Other 2,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.96,flashback,Other,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:48.96,flashback,Other,0000,0000,0000,,There's the House of Silva's second daughter,\Nwho can't even control her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.30,flashback,Other,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's training every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:56.46,flashback,Other 2,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew someone like that \Nwould be born into royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:16:01.24,flashback,Other 2,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we Vermillions are the true royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.65,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I might've just given up \Nif I were in her shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.51,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Royals mock hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:36.23,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's something only those who \Naren't born into power do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.42,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,not something that royalty does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.06,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:45.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I admire you for the hard work you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.84,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive, \Nand the weak will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:08.92,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive, \Nand the weak will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:19.43,italics,Three,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could use my grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:27.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle... Mimosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:38.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,With my big, heavy sword, I won't\Nbe able to beat his magic's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:44.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He changed the way he fights,\Nand the magic he uses while doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:52.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.94,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.20,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:23.20,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.64,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.41,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,What is that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This sword will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.12,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:23.89,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can cut through his attack magic, \Nas long as he has that recovery magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.86,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Stupidsta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:39.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first peasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,that I, a royal, ever acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,defeat that guy, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw enough at him from the both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.91,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Move. I'm going to make that girl, \Nthat weakling, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:13.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.66,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:36.42,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened? He's not \Nsupposed to have any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.33,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,A water magic attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.18,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He borrowed Noelle's powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.26,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:49.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:59.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:05.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:07.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:10.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:13.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:26.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:35.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:41.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:44.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
