Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:22:59.93,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:03.77,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Resilient
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:02.61,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:08.78,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Phoenix Robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:12.28,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it hot in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:18.54,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:25.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.75,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:31.05,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.10,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,My face itches, but I can't scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:42.65,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive, \Nand the weak will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:47.02,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Pebbles on the side of the road,\Ndisperse in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.40,main,mars,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 19:\N"Destruction and Salvation."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:55.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 19\N\N{\fs18}Destruction and Salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:53.70,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,My magic destroys all.
